### 🟡 MEDIUM

#### 5. Eager Test — `OrderProcessor_FullWorkflow_Succeeds` (line 52)

Calls **7 distinct** production methods (`ValidateOrder`, `CalculateTotal`, `ApplyDiscount`, `ReserveInventory`, `ProcessPayment`, `SendConfirmation`, `UpdateOrderHistory`) yet asserts only one outcome. When it fails, which step broke?

**Fix:** Test each method independently; if an end-to-end workflow test is desired, label it as `[TestCategory("Integration")]` and accept the broader scope.

**Risk if unfixed:** Failure diagnosis becomes a guessing game.

