#### 7. Sensitive Equality — `GetOrderSummary_ReturnsFormattedString` (line 122)

```csharp
Assert.AreEqual("Order ORD-001: 1 item(s), Total: $99.99", summary.ToString());
```

If `ToString()` formatting changes (locale, currency symbol, spacing), this test breaks even when semantics are correct. **Fix:** Assert on the summary object's properties instead:

```csharp
Assert.AreEqual("ORD-001", summary.OrderId);
Assert.AreEqual(1, summary.ItemCount);
Assert.AreEqual(99.99m, summary.Total);
```

